      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "VELOCITY GALAXY (8) flew the lids with a fast early split and went on to clock 23.75 when a 5.5 lengths winner over 407m at this track. Strong form has emerged from her last run. Can measure up again. MIMOSA MOLLY (3) wasn't far away at the finish when 5th and beaten only 4.5 lengths (24.06) at this track. Yet to win here but has run some good races. Yet to win out of this box but has been in the placings two times from three starts. A big run wouldn't surprise. WEAVING (6) looks close to another win after hitting the frame in a 10 length third (26.10) in a Grade 6/MDN at Q Lakeside. Has good speed so he should be prominent despite the draw. Expected to be in the finish again. BOONIE'S ROSE (7) comes into calculations after placing at big odds most recently.",
